Class MethodSubSignature

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.MethodSubSignature

  • public class MethodSubSignature
extends Object
    Allows one-time parsing of method subsignatures. Note that these method sub signatures are resolved, i.e. we resolve the complete types upon construction.
    Author:
    Marc Miltenberger
